    • Record

  • public class Record
extends java.lang.Object

    Title:

    CS3810 Assignment 4 External Hashing
    Author:
    [Prepared by the instructor]

    Record class

    This class defines a record which is specifically for storing in a Java random access file. See API of RandomAccessFile class in Java.

    Attributes:

    name - String, the max length is 16 chars id - String, the number of digits in id is 4.
